---
import Card from "../unitComponents/Card.astro"
---
<div class="w-full px-8 md:px-32 font-bold text-grisT mt-20">
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">SLAT CONVEYOR</h1> <br>
    <p class="text-grisT">
        The slat conveyor is a critical component in asphalt storage systems, responsible for 
        efficiently transferring hot mix from the drum or pugmill to the top of the silo. Built 
        for durability and consistent performance, it ensures heat retention and mix integrity 
        throughout the process.
    </p>
    <Card title=`Chain with a 4" pitch` contentClass="px-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-3">
        <div class="h-0.5 w-full px-6 bg-blueMain">
        </div>
        <p>
            The 4‚Äù pitch chain is a key component of the elevator, designed for heavy-duty 
            operation. With a tensile strength of 50,000 lbs (22,700 kg) and floating-type chain 
            guides to prevent jams, it ensures smooth and reliable performance, durability, 
            efficiency, and minimal maintenance.
        </p>
    </Card>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 justify-center items-center gap-6 mt-6">
        <Card title=`Optional sensors` contentClass="px-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-3">
            <div class="h-0.5 w-full px-6 bg-blueMain">
            </div>
            <p>
                Chain tension sensors and overload protection for safe and automated operation.
            </p>
        </Card>
        <Card title=`Sealed and insulated` contentClass="px-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-3">
            <div class="h-0.5 w-full px-6 bg-blueMain">
            </div>
            <p>
                Reduces dust escape and protects the mix from environmental contamination.
            </p>
        </Card>
        <Card title=`Efficient drive system` contentClass="px-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-3">
            <div class="h-0.5 w-full px-6 bg-blueMain">
            </div>
            <p>
                Equipped with an industrial-grade motor and gearbox for reliable operation.
            </p>
        </Card>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 justify-center items-center gap-10 mt-6">
        <Card title=`Heavy-duty construction` contentClass="px-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-3">
            <div class="h-0.5 w-full px-6 bg-redBg">
            </div>
            <p>
                Reinforced steel paddles mounted on dual chains, capable of handling abrasive and high-temperature materials.
            </p>
        </Card>
        <Card title=`Smooth material flow` contentClass="px-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-3">
            <div class="h-0.5 w-full px-6 bg-redBg">
            </div>
            <p>
                Optimized paddle spacing and discharge angle prevent material buildup and segregation.
            </p>
        </Card>
        <Card title=`Heat retention` contentClass="px-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-3">
            <div class="h-0.5 w-full px-6 bg-redBg">
            </div>
            <p>
                Enclosed body design minimizes temperature loss during vertical transport.
            </p>
        </Card>
        <Card title=`Maintenance access` contentClass="px-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-3">
            <div class="h-0.5 w-full px-6 bg-redBg">
            </div>
            <p>
                Top inspection doors allow quick cleaning and maintenance access.
            </p>
        </Card>
    </div>

</div>